## Architecture wins

### Eyetracker camera crate
- 4 production-grade adapters (webcam + tobii + pupil + arkit) behind feature flags
- All have synthetic sources for tests
- Heatmap output consistent across all backends
- `BackendKind` enum covers all SOTA devices

### Eventra outbox pattern
- 3 store implementations (InMemory + Postgres + SQLite)
- 1 relay with `OutboxStore` trait, `Publisher` async trait, `RelayConfig`, `RelayStats`
- Concurrent claim via `FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED` (Postgres) / `BEGIN IMMEDIATE` (SQLite)
- Jittered exponential backoff with max_attempts terminal-failure
- Graceful shutdown via `Notify` token
- Resolves #22 (no transactional publish) + #23 (no at-least-once)

### AuthKit
- Port-trait hexagonal pattern: `bind_state`/`verify_state`/`revoke_state`
- PKCE state binding middleware (FR-AUTHV-018 from Authvault GAP-008)
- OIDC Discovery + JWKS with issuer-mismatch defense + 10min cache
- JWT signature verifier (RS256/ES256/PS256/HS256)
- 11+ unit tests across the suite

### Registry (phenotype-registry)
- All 7 owned repos + AuthKit registered as `projects/*.json`
- `BOUNDARY_OWNERS.md` + `domain-roles.json` + `disposition-index.json` + `chokepoints.json` reference owned scope
- `check-ecosystem.ts` + `validate-ecosystem.sh` validate membership
- `grade.sh` with stack detection + docs-only heuristic

